t_n
s_n = \frac{n+1}{n}+\frac{n}{n-1}+...+\frac{2}{1}
t_n = \frac{1}{n}+\frac{1}{n-1}+...+\frac{1}{1}
s_n-t_n =\frac{n}{n}+\frac{n-1}{n-1}+...+\frac{1}{1}=n
s_n=n+t_n
